created a container to image as we installed python inside container not in images. hence here we are doing image from conatained with installed packages.
docker run -it ubuntu
apt update
apt install python3 -y 
docker start containerid 
docker commit  <container ID>  yourname

to store images to s3 bucket make tar backup of it write s3 commad to trasfert hr file to s3 bucket or manually we cam download.
	docker save myimage > vishal.tar
	docker load to make to untar the file

